    <link rel="stylesheet" href="${request.static_url('speedfunding:static/c3sM.css')}" type="text/css" media="screen" charset="utf-8" />
  </tal:block>
  <tal:block metal:fill-slot="middle">
    <div class="jumbotron">
      <h1 i18n:translate="speedfund-form-title">Speedfund the C3S!</h1>
    </div>
      <p class="lead" i18n:translate="speedfund-help-us">
	Help us make ends meet. Now! 
      </p>
      <hr />
  </tal:block>
  <tal:block metal:fill-slot="bottom">
    <div style="text-align:right;">
      <a href="/?en"><img src="static/images/en.png" title="English"
			  alt="switch to English language" /></a>
      <a href="/?de"><img src="static/images/de.png" title="Deutsch"
			  alt="auf deutsche Sprache umschalten" /></a>
    </div>
    <div class="row-fluid">
      <h2 i18n:translate='the-status'>The Current Status</h2>
      <p>
	<span i18n:translate='the-status-span-1'>There are</span>&nbsp;${missing_sum} &euro; 
	<span i18n:translate='the-status-span-2'>missing of</span>&nbsp;  70.000,00 &euro; 
	<span i18n:translate='the-status-span-3'>needed</span>.
      </p>
    <hr />

    <div style="text-align:left;">
      <h2 i18n:translate='the-options-h2'>The Options</h2>
      <p class="lead" i18n:translate='the-options-p1'>We have three options for you to choose from.
	The most preferred selections from our crowdfunding. Of course, you can come back more often than once.
      </p>
    </div>
    
    <hr />
    
    <!-- Example row of columns -->
    <div class="row-fluid">
      <div class="span4">
        <h2 i18n:translate='donate-money-heading'>Donate Money</h2>
        <p i18n:translate='donate-money-paragraph'>We are glad for any amount!
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-large btn-success" href="/donate">Donate by money transfer &raquo;</a></p>
	<p><a class="btn btn-large btn-warning" href="/donate?paypal">Donate via PayPal &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="span4">
        <h2 i18n:translate='tshirt-heading'>Grab a T-Shirt</h2>
        <p i18n:translate='tshirt-paragraph'>Donec id elit non mi porta gravida at eget metus. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa justo sit amet risus. Etiam porta sem malesuada magna mollis euismod. Donec sed odio dui.
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-large btn-success" href="/shirt">Pay by money transfer &raquo;</a></p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-large btn-warning" href="/shirt?paypal">Pay via PayPal &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
      <div class="span4">
        <h2 i18n:translate='shares-heading'>Buy Shares</h2>
        <p i18n:translate='shares-paragraph'>Donec sed odio dui. Cras justo odio, dapibus ac facilisis in, egestas eget quam. Vestibulum id ligula porta felis euismod semper. Fusce dapibus, tellus ac cursus commodo, tortor mauris condimentum nibh, ut fermentum massa.
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-large btn-success" href="https://yes.c3s.cc">Yes, Shares! &raquo;</a></p>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <hr />
    
    <h2 i18n:translate="speedfund-form-headline" class="deform">Your help is needed immediately!</h2>
    <!-- 
    <p i18n:translate="join-form-fill-verify-print-send">
      Please pick an option that suits you best.
    </p>
    <p i18n:translate="join-form-fill-verify-print-send">
      But first, we ask you how you want to pay. If you choose PayPal,
      we get your data from them. If you choose to transfer the money to us by yourself,
      we need to collect some basic information.
    </p>
